    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of character? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s a solid, reliable driver that gets the job done and offers a great entry point for someone looking for value. While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it still runs well and is ready to be your trusty daily companion!",
