      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising quality. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom-grade condition, reflecting a legacy of meticulous preservation and professional care. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, adheres to the highest standards of excellence. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a peerless example of engineering integrity.",
      "price": 44900.0,
